{"tid":1187501,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Huh] 往日不再 Days gone","createTime":"2019-06-05T16:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T04:13:34.000Z","uid":105546,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfb861e68df97d19c5a0bb20a213c6984a0edf7","tid":1187501,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"相隔個幾月再出新game片<br />\n今次係Days gone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我上個月已經開始上傳 但我諗住打曬先開post<br />\n費事拍幾集又開個post咁樣<br />\n第一條片係12集裏面全部抽出嚟嘅搞笑野 無興趣睇曬咁多集嘅ching希望你地睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTseMQC8xcc&amp;t=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaTseMQC8xcc%26t%3D&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=f6d35935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTseMQC8xcc&amp;t=</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全12集<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0PijUryR1BI&amp;list=PL4g-9LQx2owcaohBM6qBzlDNkM9i_nc5a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0PijUryR1BI%26list%3DPL4g-9LQx2owcaohBM6qBzlDNkM9i_nc5a&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=e014cb83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0PijUryR1BI&amp;list=PL4g-9LQx2owcaohBM6qBzlDNkM9i_nc5a</a><br />\n每集我都有個時間表,如果想睇主線嘅巴絲可以自由選擇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8dHYR0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8dHYR0.jpg&h=253035e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭2集因為當日我用youtube直播轉過去,所以無咁清同清楚,但之後我轉番做錄音就無事了<br />\n<br />\n希望大家鐘意同埋不妨訂閱支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,以下仲有舊game post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/921885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/921885</a> Hitman2全暗殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/930875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/930875</a> Hitman2只穿西裝的無聲殺手 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/950819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/950819</a> JUST CAUSE 4<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/972483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/972483</a> Devil May Cry 4<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cjjswS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cjjswS</a> 生化危機2重製(Leon)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ckmqMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ckmqMS</a> 生化危機2重製(Claire)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cnzmNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cnzmNS</a> 還願Devotion<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/crwGLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/crwGLS</a> Devil May Cry 5"},{"pid":"691bfecdefa761780fb96a49712273adaea7a400","tid":1187501,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"如果你問我隻game好唔好玩,我會話有好多bug,多到好淒涼<br />\n但反正係單機game都可以當輕鬆下,而遊戲背景都正,唔計loading要等嘅時間我都玩左30up個鍾<br />\n再講多我怕劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7d2e76edb9960019905390028453b657632afa","tid":1187501,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T23:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495f8b91a1e16fdd7677a9a233656a026b6270a4","tid":1187501,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf02605c7eddfc582590dbd0d8989ddfa89a0be0","tid":1187501,"uid":239117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T02:11:16.000Z","msg":"wfc 善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"e915c192e8cd21956f89d0a471b259768f305e81","tid":1187501,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"